Indian authorities are blaming
 Emaar Properties PJSC  and its unit Emaar MGF for problems with
facilities at the Commonwealth Games Village,  Gulf News  said,
citing officials.  Delhi Chief Minister  Sheila Dikshit  and organizing
committee chairman Suresh Kalmadi blamed the United Arab
Emiratesâ€™ biggest developer and its unit, the newspaper
reported.  Emaar external public relations declined to comment when
